Shiba the dog uses his nose and paw to open a sliding glass window at the Shimada Cigarette Shop on the outskirts of Tokyo . 
  He is trained to open the window when customers ring a bell for service at the shop . 
  Visitors have travelled from afar to see the dog and pose for photos with him . 
  One video of his customer service skills has been viewed millions of times on the internet . 
 